{"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\"/><title>Build Your Manifesto - Take The Reins</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Create your personal manifesto and share your authentic story.\"/><meta name=\"next-head-count\" content=\"4\"/><script async=\"\" src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-13DDMQLQFZ\"></script><script>\n                    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n                    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n                    gtag('js', new Date());\n                    gtag('config', 'G-13DDMQLQFZ', {\n                      page_path: window.location.pathname,\n                    });\n                  </script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/css/3b0c939fc99db33f.css\" as=\"style\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/3b0c939fc99db33f.css\" data-n-g=\"\"/><noscript data-n-css=\"\"></noscript><script defer=\"\" nomodule=\"\" src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-a146a8ef8f1e9d05.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/framework-e08ca35bb8c7d6c2.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-ecf9fdf2fdcbcf0c.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/pages/_app-a4b465d0d03c3032.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/7703-0be1e1ca03344042.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/pages/hub/members/new-3dfa2d6718fced79.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/7BvwXCOyI1muC_rGFwhKX/_buildManifest.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/7BvwXCOyI1muC_rGFwhKX/_ssgManifest.js\" defer=\"\"></script></head><body><div id=\"__next\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900\"><nav class=\"bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur border-b border-slate-700\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex justify-between items-center\"><button class=\"text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition text-sm font-medium\">← Back</button><h1 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Build Your Manifesto</h1><a href=\"/dashboard/comparison\" class=\"text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition text-sm font-medium\">📊 Job Board Scores</a></div></nav><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div class=\"bg-slate-800 border border-indigo-500/20 rounded-xl p-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">What&#x27;s a Manifesto?</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-slate-300 italic mb-4\">&quot;A public declaration of motives and intentions; a statement of principles and aims.&quot;</p><p class=\"text-slate-400\">In the context of your career, your manifesto is your authentic voice telling the world who you are—beyond a job title or resume. It&#x27;s a statement about what you believe in, what drives you, and how you show up in the world.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">Why Your Manifesto Matters</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-rose-600/20\"><span class=\"text-rose-400\">✓</span></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold\">Employers See the Real You</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm\">They don&#x27;t just want your work history—they want to understand WHO YOU ARE. Your manifesto shows them your authentic values, what drives you, and how you show up.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-600/20\"><span class=\"text-emerald-400\">✓</span></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold\">Memorable &amp; Shareable</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm\">A manifesto is 10x more memorable than a resume. Drop the link on job applications, LinkedIn, emails—anywhere you want to stand out.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600/20\"><span class=\"text-indigo-400\">✓</span></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold\">You Take a Stand</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm\">Be clear on what you believe in, what energizes you, and what you won&#x27;t compromise on. Attract people and opportunities aligned with your values.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600/20 to-rose-600/20 border border-indigo-600/50 rounded-xl p-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Want a Custom URL?</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 mb-6\">Login to get a personalized, email-based manifesto URL that&#x27;s easy to share and remember:</p><div class=\"bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6\"><code class=\"text-indigo-300 font-semibold\">takethereigns.netlify.app/manifesto/your@email.com</code></div><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6\">Perfect for LinkedIn profiles, résumés, and business cards. Or skip this and create anonymously—it&#x27;s up to you.</p><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><button class=\"flex-1 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition\">Sign Up (Free)</button><button class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition\">Log In</button></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">How We Build It Together</h2><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex gap-3 items-start\"><span class=\"text-rose-400 font-bold text-lg\">1.</span><p class=\"text-slate-300\"><strong>Answer Questions (Your Way)</strong> - We provide 7 starter questions, but you can edit them, remove ones that don&#x27;t resonate, or add your own. Make it personal.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-3 items-start\"><span class=\"text-rose-400 font-bold text-lg\">2.</span><p class=\"text-slate-300\"><strong>AI Writes Your Story</strong> - Copilot transforms your answers into a compelling manifesto that sounds like you</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-3 items-start\"><span class=\"text-rose-400 font-bold text-lg\">3.</span><p class=\"text-slate-300\"><strong>Review &amp; Customize</strong> - Read it, refine it, make it perfectly yours</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-3 items-start\"><span class=\"text-rose-400 font-bold text-lg\">4.</span><p class=\"text-slate-300\"><strong>Publish &amp; Share</strong> - Your manifesto gets its own URL. Share it anywhere.</p></div></div></div><button class=\"w-full bg-rose-600 hover:bg-rose-700 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-6 rounded-lg transition\">Start Build Your Manifesto (In Your Own Words)</button></div></div></div></div><script id=\"__NEXT_DATA__\" type=\"application/json\">{\"props\":{\"pageProps\":{}},\"page\":\"/hub/members/new\",\"query\":{},\"buildId\":\"7BvwXCOyI1muC_rGFwhKX\",\"nextExport\":true,\"autoExport\":true,\"isFallback\":false,\"scriptLoader\":[]}</script></body></html>","isFullyStaticPage":true}